      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docTitle refersTo="#adoption">Adopted by the Security Council at its <inline name="adoptionMeeting" title="5263rd">5263rd meeting</inline>, on<docDate date="2005-09-19" refersTo="#adoptionDate">19 September 2005</docDate></docTitle>
